dct_title_s: Bolivia 1:50.000: Comunidad La Purisima, hoja 5859 I. Serie H731
dct_description_sm: Inter American Geodetic Survey. North Decimal Degree -11.333333. South Decimal Degree -11.500000. East Decimal Degree -68.500000. West Decimal Degree -68.750000. Alternate title: Comunidad La Purisima, Bolivia. Relief shown by 20 m. contour interval and spot heights. Universal transverse Mercator projection. Standard map series designation: Serie H731=[Series] H731. With a key to abbreviations.
